==Useful Info==
'''Culicivoras''' are spiders with the ability to heal their allies and [[vampiric]] bites for healing themselves. They are found in the [[Spider's Nest]].

{{monster spells}}

==Tips & Tricks==

==Trivia==
Culicivoras are likely based on the real-life [https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Evarcha_culicivora Evarcha culicivora] spider, which is also known as the "vampire spider" for its habit of hunting mosquitoes that have drunk blood from other animals.

==History==
*Culicivoras were added in [[0.28]].
